{"tid":1063654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點對付公司嘅八婆男同事","createTime":"2019-03-16T02:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T03:23:02.000Z","uid":194177,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"791d74e6b779b8377cc7b1f77bf6cd8d1862424b","tid":1063654,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n公司好細，唔夠10個人<br />\n老細好撚有米，開間野過下日晨<br />\n唔蝕得多無所謂<br />\n所以大家一直以嚟都過住又輕鬆又無壓力嘅日子<br />\n<br />\n自從呢個男八婆嚟咗， 返工對我嚟講變咗係一個煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個男八婆故名思義係個男人<br />\n成日講八婆野斤斤計較貪小便宜<br />\n<br />\n1.三日唔埋兩日就提住老細幾時請食飯<br />\n有人請食飯大家都想<br />\n但唔撚係日日都提住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.成日搵機會出公數食飯<br />\n3. 間唔中就拎物資返屋企用<br />\n最難頂就係為咗合理化自己呢一種行為<br />\n成日都拉埋其他同事落水<br />\n例如自己拎咗卷紙巾就問埋隔離個師奶要唔要<br />\n<br />\n4. 日撚日都喺度問幾時加人工<br />\n其實佢真係好撚廢<br />\n都成3x歲，𢭃15K<br />\n你就知佢咩料<br />\n根本公司隨時請個fresh grad都可以代替咗佢<br />\n係佢自己選擇嚟一間咁hea嘅公司做<br />\n我有時同佢講不如你轉工啦<br />\n佢又話出面好辛苦喎<br />\n咁即係又想要人工高又要hea<br />\n三十幾歲人仲咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 仲有一樣最撚頂唔順<br />\n今日佢同我講， 你覺唔覺老細特別偏心某某同事<br />\n大佬呀 男人老狗將呢啲嘢講出口 真係好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上嗰個同事真係幾做得嘢<br />\n老細偏心佢都好正常， 正確的用詞應該係用&ldquo;睇重佢&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n當然講同事是非嗰啲真係不計其數<br />\n所以每日一返工見到佢就好撚燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解一個咁廢嘅男人仲可以喺世界上生存<br />\n有冇人身邊都有呢啲同事<br />\n點樣可以收佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42063cfda265eb789a0c09f6c120560932ee160","tid":1063654,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f37824b94b396d5982cac540af52f47cc4b992","tid":1063654,"uid":90567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"你鍾意人？"},{"pid":"494d7db0ce6f8cd0e828f943d8800cf6d7bc8bd7","tid":1063654,"uid":194177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30f37824b94b396d5982cac540af52f47cc4b992","tid":1063654,"uid":90567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:48:30.000Z","msg":"你鍾意人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"鍾意打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8d2e39351648af4e8cf9d372fdd27fd9aa7d95","tid":1063654,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"由佢吠 拉攏其他同事唔理佢 慢慢佢就唔會再吠"},{"pid":"a1724df87954a703fc1eb4bc9f2d371cdc5a31a7","tid":1063654,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"gay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6545d3f02e1da6b3ca8869e1612b0b49aed6ee1","tid":1063654,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1724df87954a703fc1eb4bc9f2d371cdc5a31a7","tid":1063654,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:56:54.000Z","msg":"gay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:57:32.000Z","msg":"我好愛我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440e3f6eeba1bd90b68043ae45b2150dddf4c46d","tid":1063654,"uid":30326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"冇人理佢一排 佢就識自己改皮<br />\n再唔係你出聲屌柒佢<br />\n利申：試過"},{"pid":"d3f380d963509912db0f9036d6871753dc007a5c","tid":1063654,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"440e3f6eeba1bd90b68043ae45b2150dddf4c46d","tid":1063654,"uid":30326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T02:57:39.000Z","msg":"冇人理佢一排 佢就識自己改皮<br />\n再唔係你出聲屌柒佢<br />\n利申：試過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:02:28.000Z","msg":"點屌法<br />\n想學野<br />\n我而家會串9佢<br />\n但d八婆恥力好強<br />\n比人串完仲笑口世世"},{"pid":"c993d5e22f3263790e5321c5e6a455cb721029c3","tid":1063654,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"請唔請清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}